item.title: Fix It Felix JR
item.description:
Fix It Felix, Jr. is a platformer video game from the film Wreck-It Ralph. Several versions of the game were released: two online versions, an Apple iPod/iPad/iPhone app, and a promotional arcade cabinet.

You needed a Windows computer with mouse and keyboard to download and to play.

press C: to insert credit
X button: Fix window
Z button: Small jump
Left arrow: Left move
Rigth arrow: Rigth move
Up arrow: Big jump
1: 1 player
2: 2 players
